Divine Secrets of the Ya-Ya Sisterhood;;2002;;PG-13;;Drama;;6.1;;Callie Khouri;;Sandra Bullock,Ellen Burstyn,Fionnula Flanagan,James Garner,Cherry Jones,Ashley Judd,Shirley Knight,Angus Macfadyen,Maggie Smith,Jacqueline McKenzie,Katy Selverstone,Kiersten Warren,David Lee Smith,Gina McKee,Matthew Settle,David Rasche,Leslie Silva,Ron Dortch;;Siddalee Walker (Sandra Bullock), a famous New York City playwright, is quoted in Time Magazine and infuriates her dramatic, Southern mother. A long-distant fight wages until her mother's friends (and members of the Ya-Ya Sisterhood) kidnap Siddalee and take her "home" to the South, where they hope to explain her mother's history and to patch up the rift between mother and daughter.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0279778/